      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Il. c. Williams attended the meet\ning of the stablemen's union last\nnight to close the charter. The initi\nalton fee was raised to $3.50 and the\nmonthly dues to 90 cents.\n\n\nThe following delegates were elect\ncd to the trades council and their\ncredentials will be presented tonight:\n\n\nCharles Hammond, +, Il. Fitzgerald\nand II. H. Garnette. Officers were\nalso elected for the coming year.\nBuck Preston was chosen president\nat large."
    }
